## Services

- Home loan broking (owner-occupied and investment)
- Refinancing
- First-home buyer guidance and strategy
- SMSF and Trust loans
- Expat and non-resident lending
- Complex finance (foreign income, visa holders, cross-border)
- Construction and renovation loans
- Borrowing capacity assessments
- Annual loan health checks

